<p>
Stick figure out feelings
<a href="https://sachachua.com/2025-03-22-02">https://sachachua.com/2025-03-22-02</a>
</p>

<p>
<a href="https://imgur.com/i-feel-emotional-word-wheel-feel-wheel-australian-english-tCWChf6">Feelings wheel by Geoffrey Roberts</a>, stick figures by Sacha Chua and the kiddo
</p>

